4Geeks Academy offers a Course in Applied Artificial Intelligence designed for professionals looking to integrate AI into their roles. This six-week program requires no prior knowledge and includes two live online classes each week, with a maximum class size of 12 participants. Instructors are experienced professionals, such as Charly Chacon, who bring real-world expertise to the course. Participants will gain insights into generative AI, context, prompts, and models, preparing them to leverage AI effectively in their workplaces. Upon completion, students will receive an official 4Geeks Completion Certificate, recognized by multiple institutions. For more information, visit [4Geeks Academy](https://4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/applied-ai-course). stop